UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 113
1 than three (3) voting members of the council shall reside in any one (1) judicial
2 district of the Kentucky Supreme Court as of the date of the appointment. However,
3 change in residency after the date of appointment shall not affect the ability to
4 serve.
5 (3) One (1) member shall be a full-time faculty member employed at a state institution
6 of postsecondary education. The faculty member shall be appointed to a four (4)
7 year term by the Governor from a list of three (3) nominees selected and submitted
8 by majority vote of the ten (10) faculty members who serve as faculty
9 representatives of the boards of trustees and boards of regents of the nine (9)
10 postsecondary education institutions.
11 (4) One (1) member shall be enrolled as a full-time student at a state institution of
